          "content": "好，根据代码梳理一下当前所有工具的完整链路：\n\n## 当前 5 个工具\n\n### 1. `search` — 搜索\n```\nWorkflow callSandbox()\n  → sandbox.exec(\"python3 /workspace/search.py 'query'\")\n    → search.py 调 Serper API（刚改的，之前是 Bing scraping）\n    → stdout: JSON [{title, url, snippet}, ...]\n  → 返回文本给 LLM\n```\n- 无截图，无浏览器\n- 纯 HTTP 调用\n\n### 2. `navigate` — 打开网页\n```\nWorkflow callSandbox()\n  → sandbox.exec(\"python3 /workspace/browse.py 'url' '/tmp/ss-xxx.png'\")\n    → Playwright 打开页面，提取 body innerText，截图保存到容器内\n    → stdout: JSON {title, url, text}\n  → sandbox.readFile(\"/tmp/ss-xxx.png\", {encoding: \"base64\"})\n  → base64 → Uint8Array → env.R2.put(\"screenshots/taskId/xxx.png\")\n  → screenshot_url = \"https://api.agents.cloudc.top/api/r2/screenshots/...\"\n  → 通过 WebSocket reportProgress 推给前端显示\n```\n- 有截图，存 R2，前端展示\n- 用 Playwright 渲染（JS 页面也能处理）\n- 文本截断到 browse.py 里的限制\n\n### 3. `extract` — CSS 选择器提取\n```\nWorkflow callSandbox()\n  → sandbox.exec(\"python3 /workspace/extract.py 'url' 'selector'\")\n    → Playwright 打开页面，querySelectorAll(selector)\n    → stdout: JSON {title, url, items: [{text, href}, ...]}\n  → 返回文本给 LLM\n```\n- 无截图\n- 用 Playwright 渲染\n- 适合提取列表、链接等结构化内容\n\n### 4. `fetch` — HTTP GET\n```\nWorkflow callSandbox()\n  → sandbox.exec(\"python3 -c 'import httpx; r=httpx.get(url); print(r.text[:8000])'\")\n  → 返回原始 HTML/文本给 LLM\n```\n- 无截图，无浏览器\n- 纯 HTTP，最快\n- 不执行 JS，适合 API、静态页面、原始文本\n\n### 5. `exec` — 执行命令\n```\nWorkflow callSandbox()\n  → sandbox.exec(command, {timeout, cwd: \"/tmp\"})\n  → 返回 stdout + stderr 给 LLM\n```\n- 任意 shell 命令\n- 有 human-in-the-loop 审批（前端弹确认框）\n- 工作目录 `/tmp`\n\n## 数据流总结\n\n```\nLLM 决策 → callSandbox() → sandbox.exec(\"python3 /workspace/xxx.py ...\")\n                                    ↓\n                            Container 内执行\n                            (Playwright / httpx / shell)\n                                    ↓\n                            stdout → JSON parse → text\n                                    ↓\n                   